    <item>
      <title>特朗普指责哈里斯在阿富汗袭击三年后撤军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/trump-blames-harris-for-afghan-exit-three-years-after-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人唐纳德·特朗普将美国从阿富汗撤军的混乱局面归咎于民主党 2024 年竞争对手卡马拉·哈里斯和总统乔·拜登，并表示他将要求参与该决定的任何政府官员立即辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/trump-blames-harris-for-afghan-exit-three-years-after-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 19:31:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
